These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
6 different pets are kept: hamster, turtle, goldfish, guinea-pig, dog, snake
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: october, march, february, november, december, july
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the owner of the snake and the person who's birthday is in october##2
5. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
9. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Pet           | hamster | turtle | snake | dog | guinea-pig    | goldfish  |
| Birthday   | july | march   | november       | december        | october | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bongani, game, baccarat, bolivar, prince
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: soccer, rowing, surfing, basketball, skiing, cycling
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is between the baccarat-smoker and the siglo-smoker##2
4. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Cigar   | bongani | prince | bolivar | baccarat | game | siglo  |
| Sport           | cycling | skiing  | soccer | rowing    | basketball  | surfing |

