.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: gospel, blues, trance, metal, pop, house
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: october, september, may, november, june, august
1. the fan gospel is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the fan metal is the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the fan pop##1
5. the fan trance is on the far right##1
6. the fan pop is between the fan metal and the person who's birthday is in october##2
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the fan metal##1
9. the fan blues is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Music-Genre         | blues | gospel | house      | pop | metal | trance      |
| Birthday   | september    | august  | october | november   | june       | may |

