.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: horror, time-travel, disaster, family, animation, documentary
6 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, snooker, mah-jongg, whist, billiard
1. the person playing snooker is the person watching family movies##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person watching horror movies is the person playing scrabble##1
6. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing scrabble and the person watching documentary movies##2
7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
8. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Movie-Genre        | time-travel    | documentary | disaster | horror | animation | family   |
| Game   | mah-jongg | whist        | monopoly  | scrabble     | billiard  | snooker |

