.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: cycling, weightlifting, volleyball, sailing, soccer, handball
6 different games are played: whist, go, domino, chess, backgammon, monopoly
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing monopoly is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person playing go##1
7. the person playing domino is the person who's sport is handball##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person playing monopoly##2
9. the person who's sport is cycling is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Sport    | cycling | handball | soccer  | sailing      | volleyball | weightlifting  |
| Game   | go  | domino    | chess | whist | backgammon | monopoly |

