.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, baseball, rowing, golf, tennis, soccer
There are 6 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, iced-tea, lemonade, fanta, mirinda
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking tea##2
4. the person who's sport is golf is the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is tennis##2
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
9. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Sport           | golf | soccer | tennis | rowing | baseball | biathlon |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | lemonade   | coffee         | tea    | mirinda     | fanta     |

