.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil, rose, daisy, amaryllis, marigold
There are 6 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, japanese, nigerian, german, argentine
 1. the person who growsmarigold is the nigerian##1
 2. the australian is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the argentine##2
 3. the brazilian is on the far left##1
 4. the nigerian is the person who growsmarigold##1
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the australian##1
 6. the nigerian is the person who growsmarigold##1
 7. the japanese is on the right of the nigerian##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Flower   | balloon-flower   | amaryllis  | daffodil | daisy | marigold | rose     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | australian | argentine    | german | nigerian | japanese |

