 6. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 7. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 8. the person playing chess is the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the person playing billiard is between the person watching sports movies and the person playing domino##2
