.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, skateboard, quad-bike, train, taxi, bus
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: aconite, zinnia, rose, lily, iris, dahlia
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 2. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is the person who growslily##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the train and the person who growsdahlia##2
 5. the person who growsrose is between the person who growsdahlia and the person driving the taxi##2
 6. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is the person driving the car##1
10. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Transport           | skateboard      | train | quad-bike | car   | bus  | taxi |
| Flower   | lily | aconite  | zinnia             | dahlia | rose | iris       |

