.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: january, june, december, august, may, april
There 6 different types of food: peas, onion, eggplant, kale, pomegranate, kiwi
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person eating kale is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 7. the person eating onion is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 9. the person eating eggplant is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in january##2
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Birthday         | august | january | june | april | may | december |
| Food   | peas | pomegranate | eggplant      | kale     | kiwi       | onion |

 